description:
Grab a fresh slice and become the life of the party with the new Golf With Your Friends Pizza Party Pack. This is the ideal set of cosmetics for a night-in and includes the following items: 

Arcade sticker
Doodle sticker
Arcade Trail
Boombox Hat
Cat Headphones Hat
Dog Earphones Hat
Pizza Hat 
Drinks Hat
Pizza Floatie
Toy Cat Floatie
name: Golf With Your Friends - Pizza Party Pack
